Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.72,0:00:10.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You are my one and only.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.68,0:00:16.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No one can take your place.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.41,0:00:21.53,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Never fade, my only flower.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.54,0:00:34.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The sun never blinds you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.88,0:00:40.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You are like a flower that blooms in shade.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.25,0:00:50.03,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Exhale those feelings you hold inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.03,0:00:59.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You are my one and only;\Nnow and forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.88,0:01:10.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The day may come\Nwhen all will rise against us,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.54,0:01:15.44,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,but I will protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.44,0:01:19.52,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Never give up, my only flower.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.52,0:01:26.11,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,TIME NOTICE THAT\NYOU SHOULD NOTICE THAT
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.25,0:01:29.90,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,NOTICE THAT THERE’S NO OTHER
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.83,0:02:26.94,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,To have fought this much,\Nand still be standing is admirable.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.73,0:02:31.95,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But the fact is that you have\Nyet to reach Bankai.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.95,0:02:34.06,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Do you wish to continue, Ichigo?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.43,0:02:36.91,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you even bother\Nasking such a stupid question?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.40,0:02:41.37,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t have time.\NCome at me with all you’ve got!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.44,0:02:46.01,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Very well! Let’s do it, Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.98,0:02:59.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,P-Please stop! Lieutenant!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.15,0:03:00.45,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Please put down your sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.98,0:03:02.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Lieutenant Abarai!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.55,0:03:26.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,R-Renji… Why are you doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.75,0:03:38.89,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Just a little farther…\Njust a little…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.06,0:03:45.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Just a little while longer now\Nand I can be there to save you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.04,0:03:53.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I will never let them execute you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.09,0:04:12.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This…Spiritual Pressure…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.04,0:04:27.37,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Kuchiki…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.18,0:04:31.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going, Renji?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.48,0:04:40.52,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’m going to…save Rukia.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.34,0:04:43.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.44,0:04:45.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’m going!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.56,0:04:52.83,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You refuse to let me pass\Nno matter what?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.33,0:04:56.95,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t intend to repeat myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.67,0:04:59.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He’s coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.44,0:05:15.56,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Senka.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.92,0:05:24.04,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A special Flash Step with a spin,\Nwhere you get behind your opponent
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.04,0:05:26.89,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,to destroy his Soul Chain and\NSoul Sleep at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.25,0:05:30.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’ve seen it countless times.\NIt’s your favorite move.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.40,0:05:35.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I knew your moves logically.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.73,0:05:39.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But now my body is fast enough\Nto counter you, at last.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.91,0:05:45.69,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Kuchiki! You can no longer\Nkill me with that sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.15,0:05:51.62,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You talk a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.96,0:05:55.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What makes you so confident?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.42,0:06:01.03,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You think you countered\Nmy sword with that level of skill?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.52,0:06:10.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Scatter.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.54,0:06:20.48,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I told you… You can’t kill me\Nwith that sword anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.09,0:06:30.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It’s not just since\NI became your lieutenant…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.65,0:06:35.83,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Long before I even joined\Nthe Thirteen Court Guard Squads…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.13,0:06:40.86,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The one I wanted to surpass…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.43,0:06:45.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,was always you, Captain Kuchiki!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.62,0:06:48.94,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You released your zanpakuto\Nwithout calling its name.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.48,0:06:51.10,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Does this mean that you..?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.53,0:06:56.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I will surpass you, Captain Kuchiki…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.24,0:07:21.02,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There’s no more time…\Nand your body has reached its limits.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.44,0:07:27.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If you continue, you may die before\Nyou reach the Bankai.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.88,0:07:31.44,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Do you still wish to continue, Ichigo?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.02,0:07:33.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ban…kai!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.27,0:08:02.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hihio Zabimaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.17,0:08:08.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You… when did you achieve Bankai?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.20,0:08:10.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, you wouldn’t have noticed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.95,0:08:12.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Not someone like you
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.16,0:08:14.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,who never pays attention\Nto anybody below him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.84,0:08:18.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll say it again!\NI’m going to save Rukia!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.75,0:08:22.48,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I said I wouldn’t repeat myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.96,0:08:26.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If you won’t let me pass…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.81,0:08:32.57,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll take you down and go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.03,0:08:34.06,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.61,0:08:38.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You won’t be able to make me fall\Non even one knee.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.30,0:09:32.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I see… its pressure is at\Nthe level of Bankai for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.23,0:09:36.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,However, it isn’t enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.62,0:09:38.48,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Scatter…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.18,0:09:40.57,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Senbonzakura!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.67,0:10:08.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Senbonzakura…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.64,0:10:12.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A thousand blades,\Neach too small for the eye to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.36,0:10:15.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,When the blades fly,\Nthey turn and reflect the sunlight,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.29,0:10:18.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,resembling a thousand\Nflower petals falling.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.56,0:10:19.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.32,0:10:26.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately for you, my sword’s joints\Nare connected by my Spiritual Pressure.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.16,0:10:27.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Your blades can’t cut through them!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.78,0:10:32.60,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Just now,\NI purposely disconnected the joints…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.99,0:10:37.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,in order to counter all of\Nyour thousand blades.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.77,0:10:43.94,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why’re you so surprised?\NI’m just telling you…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.26,0:10:47.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I can see your sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.76,0:10:53.95,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I got you down on your knee!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.33,0:10:57.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I will defeat you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.12,0:11:03.94,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s bring down the curtain,\NByakuya Kuchiki.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.40,0:11:06.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,On the battle between you and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.16,0:11:18.69,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Bring down the curtain…?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.28,0:11:28.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Very well. Then I shall bring down\Nthe curtain with my sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.01,0:11:30.48,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.11,0:11:32.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The sword that ends this…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.02,0:11:35.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,will be mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.65,0:11:44.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hado 33
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.53,0:11:46.73,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sokatsui!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.10,0:11:57.81,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He’s discarded the incantation!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.81,0:12:02.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He can do this much damage with\Na mid-level Kido without Spirit Chant?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.63,0:12:05.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You’re naïve!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.11,0:12:10.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You thought that I’d lose\Nsight of you with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.94,0:12:22.53,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! I lost control!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.20,0:12:25.11,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You’re the one that’s naïve.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.60,0:12:29.45,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I didn’t release my Kido in order to\Nobscure my movements from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.23,0:12:33.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I did it to interrupt the rhythm\Nof your Bankai.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.29,0:12:37.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The weakness of Bankai
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.26,0:12:40.10,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,lies in its sheer size\Nreflecting its Spiritual Pressure.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.94,0:12:45.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Because of its shape and size that\Nsurpasses the norm of a blade,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.28,0:12:48.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,in order to control all of\Nits movements completely,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.75,0:12:53.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,one must have over a decade\Nof training after learning Bankai.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.78,0:12:59.90,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Renji, you are not ready to\Nuse your Bankai in battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.67,0:13:03.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So what?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.44,0:13:08.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I already knew all of\Nthat when I came here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.57,0:13:11.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Luckily, my zanpakuto\Nis pretty tough!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.28,0:13:16.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Losing a joint changes nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.96,0:13:20.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Bakudo 61, Rikujokoro.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.42,0:13:23.45,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.12,0:13:28.04,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You should have simply\Nput your sword down.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.04,0:13:31.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Do you still think\Nyou can defeat me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.20,0:13:39.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Surely, you haven’t forgotten?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.31,0:13:43.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That I too have Bankai.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.51,0:13:50.70,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Bankai.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.25,0:14:23.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Scatter.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.92,0:14:26.27,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Senbonzakura Kageyoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.51,0:15:10.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A thousand blades that rise\Nfrom the ground…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.17,0:15:15.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,With their scattering,\Ninfinitely more blades then rise.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.28,0:15:18.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible to know their numbers.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.73,0:15:24.89,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible to even read their path,\Nmuch less avoid them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.13,0:15:28.57,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing to do but watch,\Nas one watches the wind pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.57,0:15:31.21,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,One can do nothing\Nbut stand there frozen,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.21,0:15:32.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,and then be swept away\Nfrom this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.57,0:15:39.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Shall I tell you the difference\Nbetween you and me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.84,0:15:42.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It’s class.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.10,0:15:53.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A beast may see the moon reflected\Non the water’s surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.92,0:15:58.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But trying to capture it will\Nonly result in sinking into the water.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.57,0:16:02.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Your fang will never reach me…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.81,0:16:05.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Never.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.31,0:16:07.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But be proud of the fact
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.31,0:16:13.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,that you were felled by this blade\Nyet you still retain a human form.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.27,0:16:29.21,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So you can still breathe?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.17,0:16:36.65,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Do not move.\NYou will only hasten your death.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.26,0:16:51.66,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It’s not over…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.96,0:16:56.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I can still…fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.69,0:17:02.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Did you not hear me?\NI told you not to move.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.96,0:17:18.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I shall compliment you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.71,0:17:23.66,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You received my Bankai\Nand are still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.33,0:17:29.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,However, if you move again,\NI will not go easy on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.34,0:17:35.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,My blades will carve you into pieces.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.72,0:17:40.66,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You must have noticed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.66,0:17:42.48,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Your Bankai is gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.32,0:17:46.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,When one’s Bankai disappears\Nagainst its master’s will,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.19,0:17:49.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,it means the master’s end is near.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.74,0:17:53.10,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Soon, you will fade away.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.66,0:17:56.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I shall ask you this once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.76,0:18:03.03,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Will you still speak nonsense\Nabout saving Rukia?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.65,0:18:10.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I can’t breathe…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.68,0:18:15.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It’s like the Spiritual Pressure\Nis turning me into ash.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.27,0:18:21.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I can’t even lift a finger…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.66,0:18:23.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I can’t…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.13,0:18:27.70,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,In the end…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.92,0:18:32.41,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,this man and I were too far apart,\Nafter all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.96,0:18:42.60,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Will you still stand, Ichigo?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.01,0:18:52.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.54,0:18:54.33,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.53,0:18:57.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I swore…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.68,0:19:00.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,…that I’d save her!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.80,0:19:03.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Swore? To whom?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.52,0:19:07.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No one…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.25,0:19:10.23,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Just on…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.95,0:19:13.11,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Just on…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.34,0:19:17.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,– my soul!\N– my soul!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.14,0:19:35.53,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Stronger than Byakuya Kuchiki?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.85,0:19:39.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What a goal you have.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.60,0:19:43.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You’d better just stay away\Nfrom her from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.26,0:19:46.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,She understands, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.34,0:19:51.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That she’s different from us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.56,0:19:54.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It’s so complicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.96,0:19:56.12,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Isn’t it annoying?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.64,0:20:01.11,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It’s always a lot harder to draw,\Nthan to tear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.91,0:20:06.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And It’s much harder to tie\Nthan to unravel.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.85,0:20:56.23,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.52,0:21:09.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Admirable.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.23,0:21:13.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Your fang…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.35,0:21:17.94,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,definitely reached me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.58,0:21:37.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Renji?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.03,0:21:41.21,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No way…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.21,0:21:45.01,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Until now, it was so powerful,\NI couldn’t figure out whose it was…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.01,0:21:48.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The Spiritual Pressure that just faded…\Ndefinitely belonged to Renji!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.28,0:21:52.95,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why? Why did you… Renji?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.56,0:22:12.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning. How are you, Rukia?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.96,0:22:15.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Gin…Ichimaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.06,0:22:30.62,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,All the days gone by\Nhave made me what I am
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.88,0:22:36.89,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Life’s not easy;\Nthat’s why I can go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.22,0:22:51.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,To the people hurrying by,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.76,0:22:55.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,“Have your dreams come true?”
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.39,0:23:00.45,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’m still struggling…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.55,0:23:10.12,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Forget returning to my youth;\NI want to live today well.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.12,0:23:15.03,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I was born timid.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.03,0:23:24.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Out where the sun shines\NI fisted my hand tight.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.22,0:23:31.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Break out of that place, that time,\Nand I can change my life
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.85,0:23:39.77,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But I could never express\Neverything deep in my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.77,0:23:45.90,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Life’s not easy;\Nthat’s why I can go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.55,0:23:54.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The rules of Squad 11!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.20,0:23:57.12,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,One, your zanpakuto must be\Na direct attack type!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.12,0:23:59.10,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,One, if you must die,\Ndie gloriously in a fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.10,0:24:01.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,One, obey the Lieutenant’s orders\Nat all costs!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.74,0:24:02.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,– Now, wait a minute!\N– Now, wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.97,0:24:04.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Any complaints, Shiny Duo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.84,0:24:06.77,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,– No giving us a duo nickname!\N– No giving us a duo nickname!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.70,0:24:20.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Squad 10 Captain,\NToshiro Hitsugaya!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.51,0:24:21.95,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You are so stuck up!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.63,0:24:25.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Squad 13 Captain,\NJushiro Ukitake!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.24,0:24:26.94,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Your long hair is against the rules!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.70,0:24:30.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Squad 6 Lieutenant,\NRenji Abarai!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.75,0:24:32.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are you challenging me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.76,0:24:35.60,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Squad 6 Captain,\NByakuya Kuchiki!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.60,0:24:36.85,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You are so cool…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.75,0:24:40.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Squad 5 Captain,\NSosuke Aizen!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.09,0:24:42.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Do those glasses have lenses in them?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.71,0:24:45.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Squad 3 Captain,\NGin Ichimaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.39,0:24:47.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wipe that smirk off your face!